  "3164790": {
    "name": "杂草丛生：花园清洁模拟器 (Overgrown)",
    "steam_appid": 3164790,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Overgrown Cleaner</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/89288103ab47c793cb33b644bd14c96b.poster.avif?t=1771870350\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/89288103ab47c793cb33b644bd14c96b.webm?t=1771870350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/89288103ab47c793cb33b644bd14c96b.mp4?t=1771870350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真是一团糟…！看起来这些地方已经多年无人打理。大自然彻底占据了一切，齐腰高的杂草、被掩埋的小路，以及隐藏在野性植被之下的遗忘角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幸好你来了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Overgrown Cleaner 中，你将在最令人满足的清理模拟体验之一里，把混乱变为秩序。放松身心，砍伐、修剪、割草，开辟穿越茂密植被的道路。没有腰酸背痛，没有时间压力，只有纯粹的修复乐趣。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>砍伐、清理、焚除！</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/8a99154323b742c5537b1ffdfdcc5463.poster.avif?t=1771870350\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/8a99154323b742c5537b1ffdfdcc5463.webm?t=1771870350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/8a99154323b742c5537b1ffdfdcc5463.mp4?t=1771870350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个地点都是全新挑战，而你拥有完全自由的处理方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如何修复每个区域，由你决定：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 清理疯长的灌木<br>• 移除枯死植物<br>• 重现被掩埋的墙体与围栏<br>• 挖掘被埋没的小径<br>• 将无法通行的灌丛变成整洁绿地</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以缓慢而细致地整理，也可以释放工具带来的全面破坏力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>探索废弃地点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/2ebc9f2bcfed8714d9d8b0613c25990f.poster.avif?t=1771870350\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/2ebc9f2bcfed8714d9d8b0613c25990f.webm?t=1771870350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/2ebc9f2bcfed8714d9d8b0613c25990f.mp4?t=1771870350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被遗忘的花园只是旅程的开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着技能提升与工具扩展，你将解锁各种被自然吞没的废弃场所：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 被藤蔓与破裂混凝土覆盖的废弃滑板公园<br>• 在入侵植被下腐朽的荒废农场<br>• 优雅被岁月掩埋的东方庭园<br>• 道路与建筑被时间吞噬的荒废村庄</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个地点都带来新的布局、秘密与修复挑战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>制作并升级强力工具</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/315c248cf47caf38545f45d9a8028277.poster.avif?t=1771870350\" width=800 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/315c248cf47caf38545f45d9a8028277.webm?t=1771870350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/315c248cf47caf38545f45d9a8028277.mp4?t=1771870350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >买不起商店设备？那正好。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集零件、废料和奇特发现，自行打造园艺机械：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 设计独特工具配置<br>• 提升动力与效率<br>• 根据你的玩法自定义装备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的手工装置很快就会超越商业设备。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>收集珍贵物品</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/9600a1d67e96dfe5ba6dc58e6a447bbc.poster.avif?t=1771870350\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/9600a1d67e96dfe5ba6dc58e6a447bbc.webm?t=1771870350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164790/extras/9600a1d67e96dfe5ba6dc58e6a447bbc.mp4?t=1771870350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >茂密植被之下隐藏的不只是杂草。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清理时请留意：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 可回收废料<br>• 可修复零件<br>• 奇特但有用的残留物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出售你的发现，为工坊升级、更好工具与未来工作提供资金。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >启动割草机，磨利刀片，夺回被自然吞没的一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>世界已被野性吞没。是时候清理了。</strong></p>",
